title: Estadio Armando Maestre Pavajeau
text: The Estadio Armando Maestre Pavajeau is a <a href="association%20football">football</a> stadium in <a href="Valledupar">Valledupar</a>, <a href="Colombia">Colombia</a>. It has a capacity of 11,000 and is the home stadium of <a href="Valledupar%20F.C.">Valledupar F.C.</a>.
